<p>
	This bath blaster is an amazing blend of mischievous essential oils that will wash away your cares and inhibitions, unleashing your hidden desires. It is an amazing blend of essential oils with warming complex overtones of pink pepper, camphor and coumarin, topped off with a neroli heart. To use simply drop your bath blaster into a bath of warm water and watch as it fizzes, releasing its perfume and essential oils. Your bath blaster can be used more than once by simply removing it from your bath when some of the bath blaster has fizzed away. This bath blaster is also suitable for vegans. Rinse bath well after use.</p>
